### OTP Backend Service - demo http tests
### Перед запуском:
### 1. Поднять PostgreSQL и применить sql/01_init.sql
### 2. Запустить backend на http://localhost:8080
### 3. Для EMAIL / TELEGRAM / SMS при необходимости настроить внешние интеграции
### 4. При необходимости скорректировать логины/пароли под свои данные

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminLogin = demo_auth_user
@adminPassword = Password123
@userLogin = otp_user_1
@userPassword = Password123

### ------------------------------------------------------------
### AUTH
### ------------------------------------------------------------

# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "login": "{{adminLogin}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

###

@adminToken = {{loginAdmin.response.body.token}}

# @name loginUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "login": "{{userLogin}}",
  "password": "{{userPassword}}"
}

###

@userToken = {{loginUser.response.body.token}}

### ------------------------------------------------------------
### USER API
### ------------------------------------------------------------

GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### ------------------------------------------------------------
### ADMIN API
### ------------------------------------------------------------

GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/otp-config
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/otp-config
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "codeLength": 6,
  "ttlSeconds": 300
}

###

GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/otp-config
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ------------------------------------------------------------
### OTP API - FILE
### ------------------------------------------------------------

# @name generateFileOtp
POST {{baseUrl}}/otp/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operationId": "http_file_1",
  "channel": "FILE"
}

###

### После выполнения запроса выше взять код из файла:
### var/otp/otp-codes.log
### и подставить его в запрос ниже вместо 000000

POST {{baseUrl}}/otp/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operationId": "http_file_1",
  "code": "000000"
}

###

### Повторная валидация того же кода должна вернуть valid=false
POST {{baseUrl}}/otp/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operationId": "http_file_1",
  "code": "000000"
}

### ------------------------------------------------------------
### OTP API - EMAIL
### ------------------------------------------------------------

POST {{baseUrl}}/otp/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operationId": "http_email_1",
  "channel": "EMAIL",
  "email": "your_email@example.com"
}

### ------------------------------------------------------------
### OTP API - TELEGRAM
### ------------------------------------------------------------

POST {{baseUrl}}/otp/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operationId": "http_tg_1",
  "channel": "TELEGRAM"
}

### ------------------------------------------------------------
### OTP API - SMS
### ------------------------------------------------------------

POST {{baseUrl}}/otp/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operationId": "http_sms_1",
  "channel": "SMS"
}

### ------------------------------------------------------------
### NEGATIVE TESTS
### ------------------------------------------------------------

### USER не должен иметь доступ к admin users
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### USER не должен иметь доступ к admin otp config
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/otp-config
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### EMAIL без email
POST {{baseUrl}}/otp/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operationId": "http_email_error_1",
  "channel": "EMAIL"
}

###

### Неверный канал
POST {{baseUrl}}/otp/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operationId": "http_bad_channel_1",
  "channel": "PIGEON"
}

###

### Повторная генерация OTP по той же операции до истечения TTL
POST {{baseUrl}}/otp/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operationId": "http_duplicate_1",
  "channel": "FILE"
}

###

POST {{baseUrl}}/otp/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operationId": "http_duplicate_1",
  "channel": "FILE"
}

### ------------------------------------------------------------
### LOGOUT
### ------------------------------------------------------------

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### После logout запрос должен вернуть ошибку
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
